<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>κυρίῳ μου <hi rend="diaeresis">υ</hi>ἱῷ Δωροθέῳ 

    <lb n="2"/>Χαιρήμων. 

    <lb n="3"/>τοῦ φρουροῦ Βαρούσιος ἀπαντή-

    <lb n="4"/>σαντος πρὸς ἐμὲ καὶ εἶπέν μοι 

    <lb n="5"/>εἶναι π<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">α</supplied>ρὰ σοὶ καὶ ἐξήτασα αὐτὸν 

    <lb n="6"/>περὶ τῶν ἀπὸ Ταμπεμοὺ <choice><corr>ἐπειδὴ</corr><sic>επιδη</sic></choice> ἐ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ζ</unclear>ή-

    <lb n="7"/>τησα τοὺς κωμάρχας ἐπὶ τῆς πόλεως καὶ 

    <lb n="8"/>οὐχ εὗρον αὐτοὺς εἰ μὴ μόνους τοὺς 

    <lb n="9"/>δύο <num value="2"/> τοὺς <choice><corr>κατακλείστους</corr><sic>κατακλιστους</sic></choice> καὶ <choice><corr>ἐγ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὼ</unclear></corr><sic>γω</sic></choice> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐ</unclear>νόμι-

    <lb n="10"/>ζον αὐτ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>ὺς ἐκβάντας καὶ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐξή</unclear>τασ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">α</supplied> 

    <lb n="11"/>αὐτὸν καὶ <choice><corr>εἶπεν</corr><sic>ιπεν</sic></choice> μὴ <choice><corr>εἶναι</corr><sic>ιναι</sic></choice> παρὰ σοί. ἐὰ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> 

    <lb n="12"/>οὖν μάθῃς ὅτι οὐκ ἐξέβησαν ἀλλ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὰ</supplied> 

    <lb n="13"/>ἔτι ἐπὶ τῆς πόλεως αὐτοὺς <choice><corr>εἶναι</corr><sic>ιναι</sic></choice> καὶ ἐ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὰ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied> 

    <lb n="14"/>μάθῃς τὸ <choice><corr>αἴτιον</corr><sic>ετιον</sic></choice> διὰ τί οὐκ ἐ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ξ</unclear>έβ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">η</unclear>-

    <lb n="15"/>σαν καὶ <choice><corr>εἰ</corr><sic>η</sic></choice> ἡ πρόφασις αὕτη, τὸ <subst><add place="inline"><choice><corr>κα-

    <lb n="16"/>τακλεῖσαί</corr><sic>κατακλισαι</sic></choice></add><del rend="corrected">καταβλισαι</del></subst> με δύο <num value="2"/> ὅτι οὐκ <choice><corr>ἐξέβαινον</corr><sic>εκβενον</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="17"/>εἰ μὴ οἱ ἄλλοι ἀπολυθῶσιν, τὰς <choice><corr>γυ-

    <lb n="18"/>ναῖκας</corr><sic><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">γ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">υ</supplied>νεκας</sic></choice> αὐτῶν <choice><corr>ἀνένεγκον</corr><sic>ανενεκκον</sic></choice> ἐπὶ τ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὴν</supplied> 

    <lb n="19"/>πόλιν καὶ <choice><corr>ἔνκλεισον</corr><sic>ενκλισον</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ἵνα</corr><sic>εινα</sic></choice> οἱ ἄρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σ</unclear>ε-

    <lb n="20"/>νες ἀπ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ολ</unclear>υθῶσιν, ὥστε νομίζω 

    <lb n="21"/>ει᾿ μὴ μωρὰ <subst><add place="inline">μωροῖς</add><del rend="corrected">μωριις</del></subst> <subst><add place="inline">τῇ</add><del rend="corrected">οη</del></subst> <choice><corr>αἰκίᾳ</corr><sic>ε<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear>ηα</sic></choice> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>υ 

    <lb n="22"/>περιπ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear><gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>σιν· εἰ δὲ τὸ ἔργον ὁδεύ-

    <lb n="23"/>ει παρὰ σοὶ <choice><corr>καὶ ἂν</corr><sic>καν</sic></choice> μὴ ἐκβῶσι ἀπαί-

    <lb n="24"/>τησον. γράψον μοι οὖν περὶ τού-

    <lb n="25"/>του· ἡ γὰρ ψελλὶς τοῦ λάκκου μου ἔπε-

    <lb n="26"/>σ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear>ν καὶ <gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="lost" unit="character"/>ιλος με <choice><corr>διώκει</corr><sic>διωκι</sic></choice> κα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὶ</supplied> διὰ τὴν 

    <lb n="27"/><choice><corr>ἀνάγκην</corr><sic>ανακκην</sic></choice> ἐξέβην. ἐρρῶσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">θαί</unclear> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σε</supplied> εὔ-

    <lb n="28"/>χομαι πολ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λ</unclear>οῖς χρόνοις. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="29"/>κυρίῳ μου υἱῷ <g type="xs"/> Δωροθέῳ 

    <lb n="30"/><g type="xs"/> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Χαιρήμων</unclear> 

    <lb n="1"/>Χωοῦ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τος</unclear> <expan><ex cert="high">δηναρίων</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">μυριάδες</ex></expan> <num value="40">μ</num><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="2"/><choice><corr>ὁμοίως</corr><sic>ομοιος</sic></choice> <expan><ex cert="high">δηναρίων</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">μυριάδες</ex></expan> <num value="600">χ</num> <num value="6000000"/>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.33719" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.33719" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="400" notBefore="301" type="textDate">IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.33719" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Gehört zum Archiv der Brüder Papnuthis und Dorotheos.</p></div><div n="meta.33719" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">48</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">3409</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">33719</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">48</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">3409</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;48;3409" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.33719" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">270</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">202</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.33719" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.33719" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.33719" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://163.1.169.40/cgi-bin/library?e=d-000-00---0POxy--00-0-0-0prompt-10---4---Document---0-1l--1-en-50---20-about---001-001-1-0utfZz-8-00031-001-1-0utfZz-8-00&amp;a=d&amp;c=POxy&amp;cl=CL5.1.14&amp;d=HASH01ac6149874c4bb5ee3d7d95"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>